<emphasis id="33A7CD77FF9A3942EF38C077FB3C5C68" box="[1033,1219,1860,1886]" italics="true" pageId="52" pageNumber="53">Signata stenzeli</emphasis>
Dante &amp; 
<bibRefCitation id="65426C94FF9A3942EE0AC077FEDE5CB4" author="Frizzell D. L." pageId="52" pageNumber="53" pagination="85 - 110" refId="ref53928" refString="Frizzell D. L. 1965. Otolith-based genera and lineages of fossil bonefishes (Clupeiformes, Albulidae). Senckenbergiana Lethaea 46 a: 85 - 110." type="book chapter" year="1965">Frizzell, 1965</bibRefCitation>
